original_title: Manhattan: Riverside Drive - St. Clair Place
text:
(1) Riverside Drive, west side, from and including St. Clair Place, showing the viaduct which extends to 135th Street.

June 14, 1931.

P. L. Sperr.

(2) The same, from a different angle, and showing the west side of the "Drive".

July 31, 1931.

P. L. Sperr.
